[vc_row][vc_column][vc_custom_heading text="Privacy Policy" font_container="tag:h3|font_size:30px|text_align:left|color:%23333333|line_height:43px" google_fonts="font_family:Montserrat%3Aregular%2C700|font_style:700%20bold%20regular%3A700%3Anormal" css=".vc_custom_1536150978588{padding-bottom: 15px !important;}"][vc_custom_heading text="Summary:" font_container="tag:h3|font_size:20px|text_align:left|color:%23333333|line_height:43px" google_fonts="font_family:Montserrat%3Aregular%2C700|font_style:700%20bold%20regular%3A700%3Anormal"][vc_column_text]business takes technology to businesses, consumers and, society in a way that makes amazing experiences possible but doesn’t come at the expense of your privacy. We believe in change and performance that supports your privacy rights and in technology designed with those rights in mind.

